"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-is-victor-wembanyama-playing-in-2024-paris-olympics-france\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"2024Paris Olympic hosts, France, will have their star man for the tournament.San Antonio Spursbig and reigning 2023-24 NBA Rookie of the Year Victor Wembanyama will play for Les Bleus.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9866641241475221, \"rank\": 0.013180034165836425, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France qualified for the Olympics as the host nation and Wembanyama will be making his Olympics debut.\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 185, \"end\": 191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9866641241475221, \"rank\": 0.013180034165836425, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wembanyama, also known as Wemby, will be leading the way for a stacked French roster.\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_men's_national_handball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998852913515, \"rank\": 8.744553990503123e-08, \"text\": \"French roster\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_men's_national_handball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_men's_national_handball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is joined by Rudy Gobert, Nicolas Batum, Bilal Coulibaly, Evan Fournier, Frank Ntilikina, Nando De Colo, Guerschon Yabusele, Andrew Albicy, Matthias Lessort, Isaia Cordinier, and Matthew Strazel.\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 391, \"end\": 402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rudy_Gobert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rudy Gobert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rudy_Gobert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rudy_Gobert\"}, {\"begin\": 404, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Batum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicolas Batum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Batum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Batum\"}, {\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enki_Bilal\", \"score\": 0.9789203048696927, \"rank\": 0.021533617216159956, \"text\": \"Bilal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enki_Bilal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enki_Bilal\"}, {\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evan Fournier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\"}, {\"begin\": 451, \"end\": 466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Ntilikina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Frank Ntilikina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Ntilikina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Ntilikina\"}, {\"begin\": 468, \"end\": 481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nando_de_Colo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nando De Colo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nando_de_Colo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nando_de_Colo\"}, {\"begin\": 503, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Albicy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Albicy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Albicy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Albicy\"}, {\"begin\": 518, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthias_Corvinus\", \"score\": 0.9386826123269126, \"rank\": 0.05360890962451571, \"text\": \"Matthias\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthias_Corvinus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthias_Corvinus\"}, {\"begin\": 536, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isa\\u00efa_Cordinier\", \"score\": 0.999999923104045, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Isaia Cordinier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isa\\u00efa_Cordinier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isa\\u00efa_Cordinier\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Head coach Vincent Collet has been playing Wemby and Gobert together in France's warm-up games.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_Collet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vincent Collet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_Collet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_Collet\"}, {\"begin\": 647, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9866641241475221, \"rank\": 0.013180034165836425, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The towering duo is, without question, the greatest interior defensive duo of all time.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Which is good, because France is going to need it.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9866641241475221, \"rank\": 0.013180034165836425, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France has top-level talent but their ability to potentially grab the gold medal - they got silver at the 2020 Tokyo Olympics - will depend on what they get out of their guards.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 811, \"end\": 817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9866641241475221, \"rank\": 0.013180034165836425, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"De Colo and Fournier remain the team's best perimeter offensive players despite both being over 30 years old and thus, struggling to stay in front of opposing guards.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 992, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colonel\", \"score\": 0.9989071842896848, \"rank\": 0.0010940112603834127, \"text\": \"Colo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colonel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colonel\"}, {\"begin\": 1001, \"end\": 1009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.150810352613031e-18, \"text\": \"Fournier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrew Albicy offers more of the same.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1156, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Albicy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Albicy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Albicy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Albicy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former New York Knicks first-round pick Ntilikina and Strazel offer more defensively but are question marks on offense and could potentially clog things up for Gobert and Wemby.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1202, \"end\": 1217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_Knicks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9933537665561642e-40, \"text\": \"New York Knicks\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_Knicks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_Knicks\"}, {\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Ntilikina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ntilikina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Ntilikina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Ntilikina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Collet used the same starting lineup in France's first two warm-up games, going with Strazel, Cordinier, and Batum alongside Wemby and Gobert.\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1414, \"end\": 1420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9866641241475221, \"rank\": 0.013180034165836425, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Batum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1980983291702682e-31, \"text\": \"Batum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Batum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Batum\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Expectations are high for France heading into the tournament, and they did come up short in both of those games.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9866641241475221, \"rank\": 0.013180034165836425, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France could opt to start one of De Color or Fournier over Strazel potentially, and potentially start Batum over Cordinier as well.\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1630, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9866641241475221, \"rank\": 0.013180034165836425, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1675, \"end\": 1683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.150810352613031e-18, \"text\": \"Fournier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \